# Code Review Plugin Settings

Copy this file to `.claude/code-review.local.md` in your project root, then customize the settings below.

> **Note:** Settings are read each time a review command runs. No restart required.

## Configuration Options

| Setting | Default | Description |
|---------|---------|-------------|
| `enabled` | `true` | Enable/disable the plugin |
| `output_dir` | `"."` | Default output directory for review files (e.g., `"./reviews"`) |
| `skip_agents` | `[]` | Agents to skip: api-contracts, architecture, bugs, compliance, error-handling, performance, security, technical-debt, test-coverage |
| `min_severity` | `"suggestion"` | Minimum severity to report: critical, major, minor, suggestion |
| `language` | `""` | Language override: nodejs, dotnet, or empty for auto-detection |
| `additional_test_patterns` | `[]` | Additional glob patterns for test files (e.g., `["**/*.spec.ts"]`) |

